{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}When a foreign order can switch off your AI, what do you actually own? · OIATC{% endblock %}
{% block description %}A US export order disabled two of the most capable AI models worldwide overnight. For First Nations, the lesson is not which model to use. It is that the model is the layer you do not own, and sovereignty lives in the data and the infrastructure you do.{% endblock %}
